title: King Arthur- Legend of the Sword[4K-2160-Ultra HD].mp4
description:
This movie is in 4K 3840*2160 Ultra HD.

To play it on your 4K TV to fully enjoy and get it's full enjoyment
you will have to either play it from your computer through HDMI
or if your 4K TV has a media player you can load it on an external storage drive 
and run it through the USB port. You will not be able to load this on a
flash drive stick. You will have to have something like a Seagate
external storage drive. 

This is awesome on a 4k tv
